THE PSL has given fans a platform to vote for their favourite Absa Premiership Goal of the Month.The fans can vote for the winning goal every month on the PSL website (www.psl.co.za). The league says the best goal of each month will be in the running for the Absa Premiership Goal of the Season award.The league has already listed 10 top goals from August until December last year.Former Orlando Pirates and Kaizer Chiefs defender Jimmy Tau hopes getting fans involved will motivate them to attend matches in their numbers.Said Tau: &ldquo;The supporters will have a say in who wins Goal of the Month and I think this will inspire them to pay attention to the games.&rdquo;